# Covalida — Default Code Owners
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners


# ── Default: all files require core review ──────────────────────────────────
*                                   @covalida/core

# ── Infrastructure & CI ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/                           @covalida/core
/.github/workflows/                 @covalida/core

# ── Community health & governance ────────────────────────────────────────────
/profile/                           @covalida/core
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                 @covalida/core
/CONTRIBUTING.md                    @covalida/core
/SUPPORT.md                         @covalida/core
/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/                    @covalida/core
/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md           @covalida/core

# ── Security & central resources (single source of truth) ────────────────────
/SECURITY.md                        @covalida/core
/docs/                              @covalida/core
/docs/RESOURCES.md                  @covalida/core
